              "type": "heading2",
              "text": "Framing Watches as Works of Art",
              "spans": []
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "text": "The Charles Zuber boutique at Yas Mall marks the brand’s first global flagship outside Switzerland. Designed at the Geneva headquarters, the Abu Dhabi boutique was envisioned as a contemporary temple of watchmaking and jewelry, blending Swiss precision with a Middle Eastern sense of luxury.",
